{"tid":1265332,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[唔係化］ Mac Pro 2019 會在中國生產　不再美國製造","createTime":"2019-06-29T06:51:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-29T09:46:44.000Z","uid":39550,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3fa3f08419d60ac0b0a519983d11f301b74260fb","tid":1265332,"uid":39550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T06:51:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">中美貿戰未解決之制，很多消息也指 Apple 有意將生產線搬離中國，從而分散風險。早前 Mac Pro 2019 發佈時竟然沒有像上一代 Mac Pro 一般強調美國製造，令人關注 Mac Pro 2019 究竟會在哪裡生產。<br />\n<br />\n今天《華爾街日報》報導指 Apple 放業在美國設廠生產 Mac Pro，改為回歸中國生產。報導指，新 Mac Pro 交由「廣達電腦」生產，現時也負責生產 MacBook。廣達的廠主要集中在中國，由於生產電腦的零件供應商都在附近，所以可令運輸成本降低。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，2012 年 Tim Cook 宣佈會在美國組裝 Mac Pro，但蘋果竟然無法在美國找不到足夠的螺絲，導致 Mac Pro 的出貨時間一再推遲數月，最終也要從中國訂螺絲才可完成整個生產程序。<br />\n<br />\n而 Apple 發言人指組裝只是整個生產流程的一個部份，而 Apple 在美國的投資創造了 200 萬個美國職位。當然，中美貿戰也會影響 Apple 的決定，若關稅被大大提升，未來有可能轉到其他地區生產。</span><br />\n<br />\nsource: <a href=\"https://www.newmobilelife.com/2019/06/29/macpro-2019-china/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newmobilelife.com%2F2019%2F06%2F29%2Fmacpro-2019-china%2F&d=FYZ0PdCaIZeH%2BWUkJYSmqx5ZC4%2B%2BlHDPeg0yH0hWprM%3D&h=74e67f8d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.newmobilelife.com/2019/06/29/macpro-2019-china/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.newmobilelife.com/2019/06/29/macpro-2019-china/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newmobilelife.com%2F2019%2F06%2F29%2Fmacpro-2019-china%2F&d=FYZ0PdCaIZeH%2BWUkJYSmqx5ZC4%2B%2BlHDPeg0yH0hWprM%3D&h=74e67f8d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.newmobilelife.com/2019/06/29/macpro-2019-china/</a><br />\n<br />\n更多限時免費情報請下載《限時情報王》<br />\n<a href=\"http://newmobile.life/ios\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewmobile.life%2Fios&d=FYZ0PdCaIZeH%2BWUkJYSmqx5ZC4%2B%2BlHDPeg0yH0hWprM%3D&h=0ecbfbb6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://newmobile.life/ios</a>"},{"pid":"e7a50c8dfc7e13c07b26e921f7a1d15fe2bf3d1e","tid":1265332,"uid":11798,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T06:52:06.000Z","msg":"ok bye"},{"pid":"61f0e3de13664c51205da0b0bf12dd16e4e2c3fa","tid":1265332,"uid":39550,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T06:52:17.000Z","msg":"屌"},{"pid":"1ab874c1456b0a34217b8285be6e6145ef00db9c","tid":1265332,"uid":1524,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T07:24:52.000Z","msg":"Tim cook真係奶共奶上癮！"},{"pid":"35a39a9d0bafa12aebe14895b6c3ea4186c6c45c","tid":1265332,"uid":23833,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T07:34:25.000Z","msg":"咁既價錢都是支那制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5be35c93d01fda4d796d9098c410dfb92b95b3d2","tid":1265332,"uid":39550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T09:46:44.000Z","msg":"叫教徒情以何堪"}]}